1
00:01:30,220 --> 00:01:32,980
[Episode 04]

2
00:01:39,590 --> 00:01:42,200
Meng Siyuan is such a hypocrite.

3
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:44,480
If he's an honest official,

4
00:01:44,950 --> 00:01:46,510
I'll eat my hat.

5
00:01:48,150 --> 00:01:49,040
Here, have an apple.

6
00:01:50,310 --> 00:01:51,640
What do you mean, Shuang?

7
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:54,760
They gave you the best ward,

8
00:01:55,310 --> 00:01:56,150
and the best medicines.

9
00:01:56,710 --> 00:01:57,430
And the medical bills

10
00:01:57,480 --> 00:01:58,560
were borne by Fang Wanzhi.

11
00:01:59,070 --> 00:02:00,310
She didn't even frown.

12
00:02:00,710 --> 00:02:02,120
You really believe Meng Siyuan's salary

13
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:03,640
can afford this?

14
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:10,630
I've asked around.

15
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,400
Han Bin wasn't badly hurt,

16
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:14,000
but he refuses to leave

17
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:16,000
so as to drain our money.

18
00:02:18,750 --> 00:02:19,590
I've been told

19
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:22,150
if we can get his forgiveness,

20
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:23,840
Yudan will get a lighter sentence.

21
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,030
I also went to his ward,

22
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,750
but he wouldn't see me,

23
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:29,430
saying I wasn't important enough.

24
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:30,190
You know

25
00:02:30,590 --> 00:02:31,280
I sell fish.

26
00:02:31,310 --> 00:02:33,150
How can I be someone important?

27
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:36,840
I was really desperate,

28
00:02:41,150 --> 00:02:42,360
so I went to your dad.

29
00:02:44,750 --> 00:02:46,360
But I didn't get to see him.

30
00:02:47,190 --> 00:02:48,400
His man said

31
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:50,840
the big project he's in charge of

32
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:52,560
is at a critical stage.

33
00:02:52,750 --> 00:02:54,630
Provincial and central officials

34
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:56,000
are all here.

35
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:57,470
He's busy managing the project

36
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:58,800
and entertaining them.

37
00:02:59,150 --> 00:03:00,470
Guess Yudan just has bad luck.

38
00:03:01,430 --> 00:03:02,870
Even Vice Mayor Meng can't help him.

39
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:31,360
What are you doing here?

40
00:03:33,030 --> 00:03:33,910
You're here alone?

41
00:03:34,430 --> 00:03:35,430
Don't you need care?

42
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,310
You're here to take care of me?

43
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:41,430
Cut the act already.

44
00:03:46,030 --> 00:03:47,030
Han Bin, you said

45
00:03:47,630 --> 00:03:48,800
we're all adults here.

46
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:50,750
What's done is done.

47
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:53,150
Let's find a solution.

48
00:03:56,430 --> 00:03:57,280
You want to negotiate?

49
00:03:57,870 --> 00:03:58,520
Excuse me,

50
00:03:59,030 --> 00:04:00,190
I'm the victim.

51
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:01,800
I won't negotiate directly with you.

52
00:04:02,590 --> 00:04:03,280
Talk to my brother.

53
00:04:32,830 --> 00:04:33,240
Hello?

54
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:37,430
Fang Wanzhi?

55
00:04:38,070 --> 00:04:39,160
What's there to talk about?

56
00:04:40,510 --> 00:04:41,830
This isn't about me.

57
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,070
I'm representing Meng Siyuan.

58
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:49,950
Come to my office then.

59
00:04:50,510 --> 00:04:51,630
Let me treat you to dinner,

60
00:04:52,270 --> 00:04:53,560
if you'll do me the honor.

61
00:05:08,750 --> 00:05:09,480
Have a seat, Mr. Han.

62
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:11,950
I've made the order.

63
00:05:11,950 --> 00:05:12,360
Please see

64
00:05:12,390 --> 00:05:13,390
if you want to add anything.

65
00:05:13,390 --> 00:05:14,680
No need. I don't have much time.

66
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,070
Let's just talk.

67
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:23,240
This is where Han Bin

68
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,390
and I had our first date.

69
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:26,750
Trying to cozy up already?

70
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:28,680
You're good.

71
00:05:29,270 --> 00:05:30,190
I was so stupid.

72
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,190
I really thought

73
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,270
our relationship

74
00:05:33,630 --> 00:05:34,750
was fate.

75
00:05:35,430 --> 00:05:36,360
Now I know

76
00:05:37,510 --> 00:05:38,600
it was all arranged by you.

77
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:39,600
You got that right,

78
00:05:40,510 --> 00:05:41,310
but not entirely.

79
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,000
My brother is a proud man.

80
00:05:43,430 --> 00:05:44,310
He refused resolutely

81
00:05:44,310 --> 00:05:45,270
before meeting you.

82
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:46,950
But once he saw you...

83
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:51,040
He's a player,

84
00:05:51,070 --> 00:05:51,830
but he

85
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:53,800
actually fell for you.

86
00:05:55,750 --> 00:05:57,680
Since you're representing
Vice Mayor Meng,

87
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,360
let's talk properly.

88
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:05,310
Vice Mayor Meng asked me to express

89
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:06,950
my sincere apology

90
00:06:07,310 --> 00:06:08,750
for what happened to Han Bin

91
00:06:09,310 --> 00:06:11,430
and send his regards
to you and your family.

92
00:06:16,270 --> 00:06:16,800
That's it?

93
00:06:17,510 --> 00:06:18,120
That's it.

94
00:06:18,830 --> 00:06:19,600
Is this a joke?

95
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:21,160
That's totally hollow.

96
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:22,240
Mr. Han,

97
00:06:22,270 --> 00:06:23,000
wait!

98
00:06:23,270 --> 00:06:25,070
I invited you in good faith.

99
00:06:25,630 --> 00:06:27,000
I just don't have much experience

100
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:28,750
negotiating with people.

101
00:06:29,310 --> 00:06:30,830
Please tell me what you want.

102
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,510
I went to Jianglin,

103
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:39,270
hoping

104
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:40,920
to be friends with Vice Mayor Meng.

105
00:06:41,190 --> 00:06:42,070
But he gave us

106
00:06:42,070 --> 00:06:43,160
the cold shoulder.

107
00:06:44,510 --> 00:06:45,310
Now you're in trouble,

108
00:06:45,510 --> 00:06:46,120
so you came to me?

109
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:48,950
My brother is a great student,

110
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,190
outstanding in every way.

111
00:06:50,430 --> 00:06:51,480
My father thinks highly of him.

112
00:06:51,950 --> 00:06:52,560
But he's swamped

113
00:06:52,630 --> 00:06:54,360
by all kinds of rumors in school now.

114
00:06:54,630 --> 00:06:55,870
He has a spot for postgraduate study.

115
00:06:57,070 --> 00:06:57,750
He can't be ruined.

116
00:06:58,560 --> 00:06:59,480
You started all this.

117
00:06:59,870 --> 00:07:00,430
Fang Wanzhi,

118
00:07:00,430 --> 00:07:01,630
aren't you going to clarify it?

119
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,830
How do you want me to do that?

120
00:07:06,750 --> 00:07:07,680
I'll take care of everything

121
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:08,800
about school.

122
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:10,560
Li Xingke

123
00:07:10,830 --> 00:07:11,750
attempted murder.

124
00:07:11,950 --> 00:07:13,510
He deserves a heavy sentence.

125
00:07:13,750 --> 00:07:15,120
You just put all the blame on him

126
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,000
and say he was insane.

127
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:17,720
He fell for you,

128
00:07:18,510 --> 00:07:19,830
followed you all the way from Yu County,

129
00:07:19,950 --> 00:07:21,120
and couldn't stand seeing you

130
00:07:21,270 --> 00:07:22,070
with Han Bin,

131
00:07:22,630 --> 00:07:23,560
so he attempted murder.

132
00:07:26,630 --> 00:07:27,950
But that's not the truth.

133
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:30,190
I'm not sure

134
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,360
the school will buy it.

135
00:07:31,510 --> 00:07:32,190
Don't worry.

136
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,430
This is the only way

137
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:35,430
for the school leaders

138
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:36,920
to excuse themselves.

139
00:07:37,870 --> 00:07:39,190
Otherwise, my brother got stabbed

140
00:07:39,190 --> 00:07:40,070
in the cafeteria.

141
00:07:40,190 --> 00:07:41,360
You think my family

142
00:07:42,190 --> 00:07:43,310
will just let it slide?

143
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:44,510
The vice principal

144
00:07:44,830 --> 00:07:45,800
and security chief

145
00:07:46,190 --> 00:07:47,360
will both be fired.

146
00:07:52,510 --> 00:07:53,720
That's impressive, Mr. Han.

147
00:07:54,270 --> 00:07:55,600
I'm helping you.

148
00:07:56,510 --> 00:07:57,950
You need to protect yourself.

149
00:07:59,070 --> 00:08:00,510
Or you'll get expelled, understand?

150
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:02,360
Do you know

151
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:03,750
why the school hasn't
questioned you yet?

152
00:08:04,310 --> 00:08:05,600
I covered for you.

153
00:08:06,830 --> 00:08:07,680
Since we might still

154
00:08:07,750 --> 00:08:08,920
reach an agreement,

155
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,120
I asked the school

156
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,070
to give you more time

157
00:08:11,510 --> 00:08:12,720
to think it over.

158
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:16,600
Fine.

159
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:18,270
I'll do as you say.

160
00:08:18,920 --> 00:08:20,510
Make sure Han Bin gets
to be a postgraduate.

161
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:21,830
This is just step one.

162
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:24,270
Now

163
00:08:24,270 --> 00:08:25,920
let's talk about something real.

164
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,720
The Jing River Bridge project...

165
00:08:32,670 --> 00:08:34,270
I hope Mr. Meng

166
00:08:34,550 --> 00:08:35,630
can endorse our company.

167
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,790
We're perfectly qualified for it.

168
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:39,840
We can bid like others.

169
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:42,200
We won't cause him trouble

170
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:42,790
in any other way.

171
00:08:43,150 --> 00:08:43,630
Besides,

172
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,480
even though you and Han Bin

173
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:46,790
didn't work out,

174
00:08:47,390 --> 00:08:48,600
if this goes well,

175
00:08:50,270 --> 00:08:51,390
I'll still reward you

176
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:52,750
for what you've done.

177
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:56,390
I'm afraid I can't do that.

178
00:08:56,390 --> 00:08:57,960
You have to.

179
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,720
Are you threatening me, Mr. Han?

180
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:07,240
Do you remember

181
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:08,360
the books Han Bin

182
00:09:08,390 --> 00:09:09,360
gave your father?

183
00:09:10,150 --> 00:09:10,840
Did you open them?

184
00:09:11,910 --> 00:09:12,440
Did you do it

185
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,550
or did Meng Siyuan?

186
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:15,750
I'm not

187
00:09:15,750 --> 00:09:16,960
begging Meng Siyuan.

188
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,840
I'm just asking you
to pass him a message.

189
00:09:19,150 --> 00:09:19,870
If he

190
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:21,270
helps us this time,

191
00:09:21,870 --> 00:09:24,080
our two families can

192
00:09:24,270 --> 00:09:25,270
be close friends.

193
00:09:26,390 --> 00:09:28,550
If he keeps pretending
to be high-and-mighty,

194
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:32,550
I'll take him down as the chief

195
00:09:32,630 --> 00:09:33,270
commander.

196
00:09:34,790 --> 00:09:35,360
There's nothing

197
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,390
I can't achieve in this world.

198
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:38,390
Let me be straight here.

199
00:09:39,630 --> 00:09:40,600
That box of books

200
00:09:41,750 --> 00:09:44,270
can ruin Meng Siyuan completely.

201
00:09:57,390 --> 00:09:57,960
Shuang,

202
00:09:58,600 --> 00:09:59,670
you talked to Fang Wanzhi?

203
00:10:01,870 --> 00:10:02,270
Yes.

204
00:10:05,150 --> 00:10:05,960
How did it go?

205
00:10:10,150 --> 00:10:11,550
As expected of someone

206
00:10:11,550 --> 00:10:13,200
raised by Meng Siyuan and Fang Jingyu,

207
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:14,550
she was brave

208
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:15,750
and flexible.

209
00:10:16,390 --> 00:10:17,120
She agreed?

210
00:10:21,630 --> 00:10:22,790
It can't be that easy!

211
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:23,790
She looks soft,

212
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,120
but she's tough inside.

213
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:26,000
True.

214
00:10:26,750 --> 00:10:27,840
She's soft yet firm.

215
00:10:28,750 --> 00:10:30,150
It would have been hard

216
00:10:30,510 --> 00:10:32,030
if you hadn't warned me.

217
00:10:33,150 --> 00:10:34,360
What she cares about most

218
00:10:34,390 --> 00:10:36,030
is Meng Siyuan's career

219
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:37,120
and reputation.

220
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:39,270
Once I spoke explicitly,

221
00:10:39,670 --> 00:10:40,840
she turned pale.

222
00:10:44,510 --> 00:10:44,870
But she's

223
00:10:44,870 --> 00:10:45,840
no pushover either.

224
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:48,200
She even haggled

225
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:49,550
over the payment.

226
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:54,080
Alright.

227
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:55,630
You won't have suffered for nothing.

228
00:10:56,270 --> 00:10:57,360
Your school will

229
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:58,240
make a move next week.

230
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:00,440
They'll hold a meeting for students

231
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:01,720
from both departments.

232
00:11:02,750 --> 00:11:04,030
Fang Wanzhi will write a self-criticism

233
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:06,150
and apologize to you publicly.

234
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:08,030
I also asked her

235
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:09,360
to state in it that

236
00:11:09,670 --> 00:11:11,790
Li Xingke planned the attack

237
00:11:11,910 --> 00:11:13,030
out of malice.

238
00:11:13,630 --> 00:11:15,840
That can be additional evidence

239
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:18,910
for the court to consider.

240
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:20,790
I hope he gets a life sentence.

241
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:14,870
It's Han Bin!

242
00:12:18,150 --> 00:12:18,790
Fang Wanzhi is here!

243
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:19,790
That's her?

244
00:12:23,750 --> 00:12:24,720
Let's see what she has to say.

245
00:12:28,510 --> 00:12:29,150
Wanzhi,

246
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:31,000
are you prepared?

247
00:12:31,510 --> 00:12:32,270
Your self-criticism

248
00:12:32,270 --> 00:12:33,750
will decide your punishment.

249
00:12:36,080 --> 00:12:37,080
Also, rumor says

250
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:39,120
the school made a deal
with the Han family.

251
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:40,790
They'll

252
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:42,360
give Han Bin an award for bravery.

253
00:12:52,910 --> 00:12:55,790
We expect Fang Wanzhi

254
00:12:56,870 --> 00:12:58,270
to reflect on herself

255
00:12:58,630 --> 00:13:00,000
deeply,

256
00:13:01,270 --> 00:13:02,550
change herself,

257
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:04,360
and start fresh.

258
00:13:05,550 --> 00:13:06,080
Alright,

259
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:08,550
that's all for now.

260
00:13:10,320 --> 00:13:11,030
Fang Wanzhi!

261
00:13:34,960 --> 00:13:36,000
My name is Fang Wanzhi.

262
00:13:37,630 --> 00:13:39,000
I'm from Yu County,

263
00:13:39,550 --> 00:13:41,320
a beautiful place with kind people.

264
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:44,440
I met Li Xingke when I was eight.

265
00:13:45,550 --> 00:13:46,790
Back then, everyone called him Yudan.

266
00:13:47,670 --> 00:13:48,870
Why did you get into a fight?

267
00:13:49,440 --> 00:13:50,550
They made fun of me.

268
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:51,790
For what?

269
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:52,790
My name.

270
00:13:53,910 --> 00:13:56,030
Li Xingke?

271
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:57,630
Yes, Li Xingke.

272
00:13:58,670 --> 00:13:59,720
Later, we both got

273
00:13:59,790 --> 00:14:01,270
into Jianglin No.1 High School.

274
00:14:02,030 --> 00:14:02,870
In there,

275
00:14:03,480 --> 00:14:05,000
we had a lot of history.

276
00:14:08,480 --> 00:14:09,960
Is this really a self-criticism?

277
00:14:11,750 --> 00:14:12,870
It's a good essay.

278
00:14:13,150 --> 00:14:14,000
A show-off.

279
00:14:14,910 --> 00:14:15,910
Back then, I didn't know

280
00:14:15,910 --> 00:14:16,910
my real identity.

281
00:14:17,670 --> 00:14:19,440
When people called me
the Princess of Yu County,

282
00:14:20,910 --> 00:14:21,720
it fed

283
00:14:21,750 --> 00:14:23,030
my vanity.

284
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:25,510
What's this "Princess of Yu County"?

285
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:27,360
It's just some silly nickname.

286
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:28,670
If you weren't always

287
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:29,630
bragging about your father,

288
00:14:29,870 --> 00:14:31,390
would people even know who you are?

289
00:14:32,440 --> 00:14:33,630
Read this word.

290
00:14:34,320 --> 00:14:35,510
Vanity.

291
00:14:36,600 --> 00:14:38,120
If you truly believe you were wrong,

292
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:40,150
fill every one of these pages.

293
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:42,320
When I was a sophomore,

294
00:14:42,960 --> 00:14:44,630
