00:26:49,590 --> 00:26:51,480
Is my father in the county office?

594
00:26:53,160 --> 00:26:54,160
No?

595
00:26:56,640 --> 00:26:57,350
Wanzhi,

596
00:26:57,960 --> 00:26:59,000
don't worry.

597
00:26:59,510 --> 00:27:00,550
Maybe he was

598
00:27:00,550 --> 00:27:01,830
called in for work.

599
00:27:02,550 --> 00:27:03,640
Let's eat first.

600
00:27:03,920 --> 00:27:05,070
You haven't eaten all day.

601
00:28:02,790 --> 00:28:03,310
Dad,

602
00:28:04,830 --> 00:28:06,200
you've been here all night?

603
00:28:07,880 --> 00:28:09,000
Why didn't you come home?

604
00:28:13,000 --> 00:28:14,270
I was reflecting on myself.

605
00:28:15,440 --> 00:28:16,550
I, Meng Siyuan,

606
00:28:18,480 --> 00:28:19,200
an official

607
00:28:19,200 --> 00:28:20,590
trained by the Party for years,

608
00:28:23,000 --> 00:28:25,030
have failed at my job,

609
00:28:26,590 --> 00:28:27,480
failed to teach

610
00:28:27,480 --> 00:28:28,590
my daughter well,

611
00:28:30,550 --> 00:28:32,310
and let Fang Jingyu down.

612
00:28:39,720 --> 00:28:40,480
I know

613
00:28:42,240 --> 00:28:43,790
times have changed.

614
00:28:45,720 --> 00:28:46,350
Money

615
00:28:47,790 --> 00:28:49,030
matters more and more now.

616
00:28:53,880 --> 00:28:55,310
Your mother left you

617
00:28:55,350 --> 00:28:56,440
all her savings.

618
00:28:58,920 --> 00:28:59,880
Isn't that enough?

619
00:29:02,880 --> 00:29:04,510
You said you made a mistake before

620
00:29:05,400 --> 00:29:06,720
and were too ashamed to see me.

621
00:29:09,440 --> 00:29:10,310
I believed you.

622
00:29:12,030 --> 00:29:12,750
All these days,

623
00:29:12,790 --> 00:29:14,070
I've worried about you.

624
00:29:17,110 --> 00:29:18,440
I was afraid you were too sad.

625
00:29:20,110 --> 00:29:21,350
But now I see.

626
00:29:23,310 --> 00:29:24,880
I was just being sentimental.

627
00:29:27,070 --> 00:29:27,830
You deliberately

628
00:29:27,960 --> 00:29:28,880
avoided me.

629
00:29:30,550 --> 00:29:32,400
You brought a box of books home

630
00:29:33,000 --> 00:29:33,680
to trap me

631
00:29:33,790 --> 00:29:35,240
with the Han family, didn't you?

632
00:29:41,640 --> 00:29:43,030
Do you know what was

633
00:29:45,350 --> 00:29:46,400
in that box?

634
00:29:48,640 --> 00:29:49,270
Money.

635
00:29:52,030 --> 00:29:53,270
Five hundred thousand in cash.

636
00:29:54,440 --> 00:29:55,550
Your mother and I have never

637
00:29:55,590 --> 00:29:57,240
seen that much money in our lives.

638
00:29:58,200 --> 00:29:59,640
What would I be if I took it?

639
00:30:00,070 --> 00:30:01,510
That would be a breach
of duty and bribery!

640
00:30:01,750 --> 00:30:03,680
I'd be sent to prison and punished!

641
00:30:06,030 --> 00:30:06,830
Fang Jingyu

642
00:30:06,880 --> 00:30:08,270
raised you.

643
00:30:08,960 --> 00:30:11,030
How could you do this?

644
00:30:12,110 --> 00:30:12,830
If

645
00:30:14,000 --> 00:30:16,030
it's because I've been cold to you

646
00:30:16,110 --> 00:30:17,200
since she passed away,

647
00:30:17,550 --> 00:30:18,200
I apologize.

648
00:30:18,680 --> 00:30:19,960
I apologize to you now.

649
00:30:20,270 --> 00:30:21,030
I'm sorry.

650
00:30:21,830 --> 00:30:22,590
I'm sorry!

651
00:30:22,720 --> 00:30:23,200
Dad!

652
00:30:23,640 --> 00:30:24,350
Dad, please don't!

653
00:30:24,350 --> 00:30:25,310
You want to kneel? Fine.

654
00:30:25,510 --> 00:30:26,750
Kneel here.

655
00:30:27,310 --> 00:30:28,830
Kneel to your mother's grave!

656
00:30:29,920 --> 00:30:30,790
Do you know

657
00:30:31,880 --> 00:30:32,830
how much the Fang family

658
00:30:32,920 --> 00:30:34,590
has done for Yu County
for generations?

659
00:30:35,640 --> 00:30:36,400
Your mother...

660
00:30:37,830 --> 00:30:38,510
How many good deeds

661
00:30:38,550 --> 00:30:39,510
did she do in her life?

662
00:30:39,590 --> 00:30:40,680
How many people did she save?

663
00:30:41,510 --> 00:30:42,510
Are you trying

664
00:30:43,030 --> 00:30:44,720
to destroy our family's reputation?

665
00:30:50,440 --> 00:30:51,640
Think for yourself.

666
00:30:53,880 --> 00:30:55,400
Do you deserve this?

667
00:31:03,440 --> 00:31:04,720
Tell the Han family for me.

668
00:31:07,440 --> 00:31:08,550
I am a Party member.

669
00:31:09,590 --> 00:31:10,590
I have principles.

670
00:31:12,640 --> 00:31:14,200
I'm not afraid to fight them to the end.

671
00:31:15,030 --> 00:31:16,550
I've already prepared my resignation.

672
00:31:17,790 --> 00:31:19,110
I'm stepping down as chief commander.

673
00:31:20,110 --> 00:31:21,270
As long as I'm in office,

674
00:31:22,160 --> 00:31:22,880
the Han family

675
00:31:23,680 --> 00:31:24,720
will not take a dime

676
00:31:25,110 --> 00:31:26,590
from our country!

677
00:31:28,830 --> 00:31:29,720
Dad! Dad!

678
00:31:29,750 --> 00:31:30,480
Don't call me that!

679
00:31:32,200 --> 00:31:33,200
I don't deserve

680
00:31:34,350 --> 00:31:35,160
that title.

681
00:31:48,720 --> 00:31:49,510
Don't call me that!

682
00:31:51,200 --> 00:31:52,310
I don't deserve

683
00:31:53,440 --> 00:31:54,400
that title.

684
00:32:10,680 --> 00:32:11,270
Wanzhi!

685
00:32:12,440 --> 00:32:13,440
Wanzhi, don't leave!

686
00:32:14,000 --> 00:32:15,920
Explain to your dad when he comes home!

687
00:32:16,440 --> 00:32:17,110
Wanzhi!

688
00:32:17,960 --> 00:32:18,510
Grandma Yu.

689
00:32:19,160 --> 00:32:19,680
By the way,

690
00:32:20,880 --> 00:32:21,240
Grandma Yu,

691
00:32:21,240 --> 00:32:22,790
please give this tape to him.

692
00:32:23,310 --> 00:32:24,920
I won't. You give it yourself.

693
00:32:25,310 --> 00:32:25,960
Explain everything

694
00:32:26,070 --> 00:32:27,400
to him face to face.

695
00:32:27,550 --> 00:32:29,550
Don't let it come between you two.

696
00:32:32,750 --> 00:32:34,070
Please, you have to.

697
00:32:34,750 --> 00:32:36,680
Tell him this will clear his name.

698
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:41,720
Grandma Yu,

699
00:32:42,510 --> 00:32:43,200
I'm leaving.

700
00:32:44,110 --> 00:32:45,400
I don't think I'll come back.

701
00:32:46,200 --> 00:32:47,310
Take care.

702
00:32:49,030 --> 00:32:49,640
Wanzhi!

703
00:32:50,240 --> 00:32:50,790
Wanzhi!

704
00:32:51,750 --> 00:32:52,590
Wanzhi!

705
00:32:53,110 --> 00:32:54,830
Where are you going?

706
00:32:55,160 --> 00:32:56,440
Wanzhi!

707
00:32:57,400 --> 00:32:57,960
What?

708
00:32:58,350 --> 00:32:59,200
Shenzhen?

709
00:33:03,960 --> 00:33:05,640
There's a trendy word for it now:

710
00:33:06,110 --> 00:33:06,960
chasing opportunities.

711
00:33:08,160 --> 00:33:09,030
Wish me luck.

712
00:33:09,680 --> 00:33:10,440
Why do you go that far?

713
00:33:10,750 --> 00:33:11,350
Your speech

714
00:33:11,350 --> 00:33:12,640
shocked the school leaders.

715
00:33:13,440 --> 00:33:14,240
Rumor is

716
00:33:14,510 --> 00:33:15,550
they don't dare to punish you.

717
00:33:16,270 --> 00:33:16,830
But I don't want

718
00:33:16,880 --> 00:33:18,790
to live with everyone
whispering about me.

719
00:33:19,480 --> 00:33:20,640
Come on!

720
00:33:20,680 --> 00:33:21,350
Just drop this

721
00:33:21,350 --> 00:33:23,070
"Princess of Yu County" act.

722
00:33:24,750 --> 00:33:25,440
There's no

723
00:33:25,510 --> 00:33:26,790
princess anymore.

724
00:33:27,750 --> 00:33:29,200
The whole thing is too complicated.

725
00:33:30,550 --> 00:33:31,920
I can't explain it.

726
00:33:32,830 --> 00:33:33,720
He probably

727
00:33:35,880 --> 00:33:36,960
won't forgive me.

728
00:33:38,790 --> 00:33:40,030
He might even publicly

729
00:33:40,240 --> 00:33:41,440
disown me.

730
00:33:42,440 --> 00:33:43,590
Don't be so pessimistic.

731
00:33:44,070 --> 00:33:45,400
You were tricked too.

732
00:33:45,880 --> 00:33:47,310
Write your dad a letter and explain.

733
00:33:49,510 --> 00:33:51,510
Disowning me might be

734
00:33:52,680 --> 00:33:54,030
the best choice for him.

735
00:33:54,920 --> 00:33:55,920
I can't be the one

736
00:33:57,000 --> 00:33:58,680
who ruins his political future.

737
00:33:59,880 --> 00:34:01,110
Don't talk like that.

738
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:03,310
He's not just my dad.

739
00:34:05,240 --> 00:34:06,310
He's my savior.

740
00:34:09,030 --> 00:34:10,150
I can't implicate him.

741
00:34:11,230 --> 00:34:12,800
I've thought it over.

742
00:34:14,190 --> 00:34:15,110
I have to stand on

743
00:34:16,070 --> 00:34:17,000
my own two feet now.

744
00:34:19,190 --> 00:34:20,030
Wherever I end up,

745
00:34:20,360 --> 00:34:21,550
whatever I become,

746
00:34:24,360 --> 00:34:25,190
it's all my fate.

747
00:34:47,710 --> 00:34:50,960
(Instead of struggling between
blood ties and gratitude,)

748
00:34:51,360 --> 00:34:53,320
(I might as well pull
myself up by the roots)

749
00:34:53,710 --> 00:34:55,400
(and find new soil.)

750
00:34:56,360 --> 00:34:57,480
(In 1995,)

751
00:34:57,670 --> 00:34:59,000
(I drifted like a speck of dust)

752
00:34:59,230 --> 00:35:01,480
(to a completely new city,)

753
00:35:02,000 --> 00:35:02,800
(Shenzhen.)

754
00:35:03,960 --> 00:35:04,960
(My mom used to say)

755
00:35:04,960 --> 00:35:06,030
(that a person had three fates.)

756
00:35:06,800 --> 00:35:08,230
(Heavenly Fate is already in the past)

757
00:35:08,480 --> 00:35:09,320
(and can't be changed.)

758
00:35:09,920 --> 00:35:12,000
(Now I'll use my Real Fate
and Self-made Fate)

759
00:35:12,280 --> 00:35:13,840
(to prove my worth.)

760
00:35:15,480 --> 00:35:17,360
(This city doesn't care
where you're from,)

761
00:35:17,510 --> 00:35:18,480
(only how hard you work.)

762
00:35:19,440 --> 00:35:20,840
(My bag is empty,)

763
00:35:21,030 --> 00:35:23,190
(but it can carry my whole future.)

764
00:35:24,590 --> 00:35:26,320
(The fast pace hits me at once.)

765
00:35:26,320 --> 00:35:28,480
(I have no time to admire the city.)

766
00:35:28,670 --> 00:35:30,510
(I have to find a job)

767
00:35:30,510 --> 00:35:32,070
(to support myself immediately.)

768
00:35:33,480 --> 00:35:35,320
(Countless people like me)

769
00:35:35,320 --> 00:35:36,630
(are flowing into)

770
00:35:36,800 --> 00:35:38,550
(this land that is destined to shine.)

771
00:35:53,480 --> 00:35:54,710
Sir, how do I sign up?

772
00:35:54,840 --> 00:35:55,230
Your resume.

773
00:35:55,510 --> 00:35:56,360
I have no resume.

774
00:35:56,510 --> 00:35:57,230
Get one.

775
00:35:57,400 --> 00:35:58,630
Make sure you fill in a phone number.

776
00:35:58,800 --> 00:36:00,110
It must be a local number.

777
00:36:00,400 --> 00:36:00,920
Or residence.

778
00:36:01,150 --> 00:36:02,030
Sir, I have a bachelor's

779
00:36:02,030 --> 00:36:02,360
degree.

780
00:36:02,360 --> 00:36:03,150
Sir, I have...

781
00:36:03,360 --> 00:36:04,510
I have a registration number!

782
00:36:04,510 --> 00:36:05,320
Look at me, boss!

783
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:20,630
Miss,

784
00:36:21,880 --> 00:36:22,510
you like it?

785
00:36:23,670 --> 00:36:24,800
I can give it to you.

786
00:36:25,150 --> 00:36:25,510
No, thanks.

787
00:36:26,230 --> 00:36:27,230
What's your problem?

788
00:36:27,400 --> 00:36:29,630
You're the one staring at me.

789
00:36:29,840 --> 00:36:31,320
Take it if you like it.

790
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:48,070
Why are there two prices?

791
00:36:49,440 --> 00:36:50,590
You can pick the cheaper one,

792
00:36:51,110 --> 00:36:52,630
but that one doesn't
include answering calls.

793
00:36:53,480 --> 00:36:54,150
I'll take the other.

794
00:36:56,880 --> 00:36:57,840
You're here for a job, right?

795
00:36:58,230 --> 00:36:59,110
We have a copier.

796
00:36:59,670 --> 00:37:00,400
It's cheaper to copy

797
00:37:00,400 --> 00:37:01,510
resumes here than outside.

798
00:37:03,110 --> 00:37:03,880
Great!

799
00:37:05,150 --> 00:37:05,480
Come on.

800
00:37:09,480 --> 00:37:10,400
This is your bed.

801
00:37:11,800 --> 00:37:12,550
Here's the key.

802
00:38:05,510 --> 00:38:06,230
You're new here?

803
00:38:07,030 --> 00:38:07,590
Hello.

804
00:38:07,960 --> 00:38:08,440
Hi.

805
00:38:10,360 --> 00:38:11,480
Nice bed you got.

806
00:38:11,800 --> 00:38:12,840
The last girl stayed two nights

807
00:38:12,920 --> 00:38:13,840
and got a job.

808
00:38:14,070 --> 00:38:15,190
That company offered her a place

809
00:38:15,230 --> 00:38:16,360
and a monthly salary of over 2,000.

810
00:38:16,710 --> 00:38:17,550
That much?

811
00:38:17,920 --> 00:38:20,030
She has a Tsinghua master's degree.

812
00:38:22,280 --> 00:38:24,000
I have a bachelor's from
Zhejiang University,

813
00:38:24,280 --> 00:38:25,880
and I also got two offers.

814
00:38:26,440 --> 00:38:27,760
But the pay isn't good.

815
00:38:28,360 --> 00:38:29,280
So I'm still looking.

816
00:38:31,670 --> 00:38:32,670
Which college did you go to?

817
00:38:32,840 --> 00:38:33,550
What's your degree?

818
00:38:36,710 --> 00:38:37,320
I...

819
00:38:38,880 --> 00:38:40,320
It's okay if you're not
from a top school.

820
00:38:40,480 --> 00:38:41,280
You'll get a job as long

821
00:38:41,440 --> 00:38:42,550
as you have a college degree.

822
00:39:00,550 --> 00:39:00,920
Sir,

823
00:39:01,000 --> 00:39:02,280
please look at my resume.

824
00:39:03,440 --> 00:39:04,590
Sir, this is my resume.

825
00:39:04,630 --> 00:39:05,480
Please take a look.

826
00:39:05,920 --> 00:39:07,230
Sir, here's my resume.

827
00:39:07,960 --> 00:39:08,840
Hello, here's my resume.

828
00:39:08,840 --> 00:39:09,510
Please have a look.

829
00:39:09,510 --> 00:39:10,280
My number is on it.

830
00:39:10,510 --> 00:39:11,030
Hello,

831
00:39:11,230 --> 00:39:11,550
sir!

832
00:39:11,550 --> 00:39:12,670
This is my resume!

833
00:39:18,960 --> 00:39:20,760
Stop waiting around.

834
00:39:21,400 --> 00:39:22,800
I'll let you know if someone calls.

835
00:39:25,150 --> 00:39:26,630
Thank you.

836
00:39:33,840 --> 00:39:34,510
You're back.

837
00:39:35,480 --> 00:39:36,230
You're leaving?

838
00:39:37,000 --> 00:39:37,880
I got a job.

839
00:39:39,590 --> 00:39:40,510
They offered me a dormitory.

840
00:39:41,400 --> 00:39:43,000
I can't keep staying here.

841
00:39:43,550 --> 00:39:45,440
I'll take this job and look
for something better.

842
00:39:48,400 --> 00:39:49,400
Don't be too picky.

843
00:39:50,150 --> 00:39:50,800
Good luck.

844
00:40:22,190 --> 00:40:22,670
Thanks.

845
00:40:23,110 --> 00:40:24,550
No problem. It's my pleasure.

846
00:40:25,000 --> 00:40:25,710
Home needs parents;

847
00:40:25,710 --> 00:40:26,550
the world needs friends.

848
00:40:29,760 --> 00:40:30,630
Good writing.

849
00:40:31,760 --> 00:40:32,480
Thanks.

850
00:40:37,190 --> 00:40:39,360
But you can't fake your education.

851
00:40:42,230 --> 00:40:43,840
I did go to this university.

852
00:40:44,440 --> 00:40:45,480
Then why didn't you fill

853
00:40:45,510 --> 00:40:46,710
that blank earlier?

854
00:40:47,110 --> 00:40:48,400
Did you forget it before?

855
00:40:49,110 --> 00:40:50,070
How is that possible?

856
00:40:50,670 --> 00:40:51,880
Four years of undergrad,

857
00:40:53,280 --> 00:40:54,360
but you've only finished

858
00:40:54,360 --> 00:40:55,280
two and a half years.

859
00:40:56,320 --> 00:40:57,440
I just didn't finish it all.

860
00:41:00,110 --> 00:41:01,440
Dropout or expelled?

861
00:41:03,840 --> 00:41:05,110
You don't have to say.

862
00:41:05,510 --> 00:41:06,110
You didn't finish,

863
00:41:06,280 --> 00:41:06,880
so you can't put

864
00:41:07,030 --> 00:41:08,150
bachelor's degree there.

865
00:41:08,320 --> 00:41:09,280
If they find out,

866
00:41:09,440 --> 00:41:10,150
you'll be blacklisted,

867
00:41:10,320 --> 00:41:11,630
which will ruin your future career.

868
00:41:11,710 --> 00:41:12,190
Your pen.

869
00:41:13,000 --> 00:41:14,000
There's one more form to fill.

870
00:41:14,630 --> 00:41:15,190
I'm done.

871
00:41:16,510 --> 00:41:17,630
Actually, you can still

872
00:41:17,710 --> 00:41:19,150
make it without a degree.

873
00:41:20,190 --> 00:41:20,800
Come with me.

874
00:41:22,360 --> 00:41:22,800
Come on.

875
00:41:39,920 --> 00:41:40,550
Sir,

876
00:41:41,000 --> 00:41:42,590
what position are you offering here?

877
00:41:42,960 --> 00:41:44,030
I studied education.

878
00:41:44,070 --> 00:41:44,880
It's a perfect match.

879
00:41:45,190 --> 00:41:46,150
I didn't graduate,

880
00:41:46,150 --> 00:41:47,590
but I have my transcripts from the first

881
00:41:47,590 --> 00:41:48,150
three years.

882
00:41:48,150 --> 00:41:49,360
All my grades were A's.

883
00:41:49,840 --> 00:41:50,360
My dream

884
00:41:50,440 --> 00:41:51,360
